<div class="privacy-policy bg-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">

       <div class="policy-box">

  <p class="mb-4 text-muted">
    Last updated: <%= new Date().toDateString() %>
  </p>

  <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
  <p>
    We collect essential information such as your name, email address, and optionally your phone number when you register or interact with our platform. In addition, we may collect basic device and usage data (such as browser type and activity on the site) to help us understand user behavior and improve our services.
  </p>

  <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
  <p>
    Your information is used to create and manage your account, provide access to purchased courses or plans, process transactions, and communicate important updates. We may also use this data to enhance platform performance and personalize your experience.
  </p>

  <h4>3. Authentication & Security</h4>
  <p>
    We use OTP-based authentication to provide a secure login experience. Your data is handled with appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, while we strive to protect your data, no system can be completely secure.
  </p>

  <h4>4. Payments</h4>
  <p>
    All payments are processed through secure and trusted third-party payment providers. We do not store your card details, banking information, or sensitive payment data on our servers.
  </p>

  <h4>5. Data Sharing</h4>
  <p>
    We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. Data may be shared only with trusted third-party services such as payment gateways or when required by law or legal processes.
  </p>

  <h4>6. Cookies</h4>
  <p>
    Our platform may use cookies to improve functionality, remember user preferences, and maintain active sessions. These cookies help deliver a smoother and more personalized browsing experience.
  </p>

  <h4>7. Your Rights</h4>
  <p>
    You have the right to access and update your personal information at any time through your account. You may also request deletion of your data by contacting us, subject to any legal or operational requirements.
  </p>

  <h4>8. Updates to Policy</h4>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Continued use of the platform after updates indicates your acceptance of the revised policy.
  </p>

  <h4>9. Contact Us</h4>
  <p>
    If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy, you can contact us at:
    <br />
    <strong>shonytalks@gmail.com</strong>
  </p>

</div>

